nd":"text","text":"(Kull;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one who directs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rightly directs, another;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an indicator;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a discoverer:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing by which one is directed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"guided,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yusotadal~u bihi","text_ar":"مَا يُسْتَدَلُّ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"S, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which one is rightly directed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an indication; an evidence; a proof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an argument;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sign set up for the knowledge of a thing indicated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(whence smoke is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylN EalaY Aln~aAri","text_ar":"دَلِيلٌ عَلَى النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an indication of fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"];)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"anything whereby a thing indicated is known, whether relating to an object of sense or to the law"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"decisive or indecisive:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalaAlapN","text_ar":"دَلَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylN","text_ar":"دَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", because a thing is called by the inf. n. of its verb: (Kull:) and so is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dil~iylaY","text_ar":"دِلِّيلَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, MF, TA,) though this is asserted in the K to have been said heedlessly by J because this last word is an inf. n.; for the inf. n. is used in the sense of the act. part. n., almost by a general rule, as it is also in the sense of the pass. part. n.: (MF, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylN","text_ar":"دَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adil~aA='u","text_ar":"اَدِلَّا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally restricted to rational beings, or always so restricted,] and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adil~apN","text_ar":"اَدِلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[generally restricted to things by which one is directed &c., but properly a pl. of pauc.,] (M, TA) and, accord. to some,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalaAy^ilu","text_ar":"دَلَايِلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Kull,) or this is pl. of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylapN","text_ar":"دَلِيلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[fem. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daliylN","text_ar":"دَلِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalaAlapN","text_ar":"دَلَالَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as is also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dalaAlaAtN","text_ar":"دَلَالَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA daliyla AlmutaHay~iriyna","text_ar":"يَا دَلِيلَ المُتَحَيِّرِينَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O guide of those who are perplexed"},{"kind":"text","text":"to that by means of which their perplexity will depart. (Kull.) The saying of a poet,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"$ad~uwA AlmaTaY EalaY daliylK daAy^ibi"},{"kind":"text","text":"means, as some say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaliylK","text_ar":"بِدَلِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i.e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They bound the saddles upon the camels for riding, with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of, a toiling guide"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or, accord. to IJ, it may be elliptical, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaYdilaAlapi daliylK","text_ar":"عَلَىدِلَالَةِ دَلِيلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and is like the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siro EalaY A@somi A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"سِرْ عَلَى ا@سْمِ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as though he said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEotamidiyna EalaY daliylK daAy^ibi","text_ar":"مُعْتَمِدِينَ عَلَى دَلِيلٍ دَايِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relying upon a toiling guide"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","Kull","TA","S","MF","M"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}